sequenceDiagram
  actor Reader
  participant Web as Nextjs Web
  participant API as FastAPI API
  participant Cache as Redis Cache
  participant DB as Postgres SQLite
  participant Infer as Inference Service
  participant LLM as Vertex AI

  Reader->>Web: Open home
  Web->>API: GET /api/articles
  API->>Cache: Get cached list
  alt cache hit
    Cache-->>API: summaries
  else cache miss
    API->>DB: Query articles and summaries
    alt summary missing
      API->>Infer: Generate summary
      alt qc fail
        Infer->>LLM: Fallback summary
        LLM-->>Infer: summary
      end
      Infer-->>API: summary
      API->>DB: Store summary
    end
    DB-->>API: results
    API->>Cache: Set cache
  end
  API-->>Web: Response
  Web-->>Reader: Render list
